# Personal data — TRACKED in this fork on purpose (see no-publishing-fork memory /
# .github/workflows/no-user-data.yml). This fork exists to back up the user's own
# CV, profile, tracker, reports, etc. in their own private remote. The CI guard
# (no-user-data.yml) is what stops any of this from ever landing in a PR/merge to
# the upstream santifer/career-ops repo — push to `upstream` is also disabled at
# the remote level (see `git remote -v`) and blocked by a local pre-push hook.
#
# If you are NOT the fork owner and cloned this as a fresh install, note that a
# stock career-ops checkout normally ignores all of the paths below — see
# DATA_CONTRACT.md for the general-case data contract.

# Personal documents — never commit scans or copies of these (PII).
# Catches common identity/credential filenames so they can't be staged by accident.
*passport*
*diploma*
*简历*
*学位*
*成绩单*

# Secrets (never commit — use .env.example as template)
.env
# Universal safety net — protects ALL checkouts/branches, incl. untracked subprojects
# (e.g. web/ before it graduates to main). Never commit local env files or TS build caches.
**/.env.local
**/.env*.local
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Generated
.resolved-prompt-*
node_modules/
bun.lock
# Report-number reservation sentinels (ephemeral, created by reserve-report-num.mjs)
reports/*-RESERVED.md

# Backup files written by normalize-statuses.mjs / dedup-tracker.mjs
*.bak

# Batch — ephemeral working artifacts, not durable personal-data backup
batch/logs/*
!batch/logs/.gitkeep
batch/batch-state.tsv
batch/batch-input.tsv
batch/tracker-additions/**/*.tsv
!batch/tracker-additions/.gitkeep

# Local update-checker state (not personal data, just operational flags)
.update-dismissed
.update-lock

# OS
.DS_Store
*.mov
*.mp4

# CLI-specific local config (machine-local only — never synced, even to your own backup)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/memory/
.opencode/settings.local.json
.opencode/memory/
career-dashboard
career-dashboard.exe
package-lock.json
!web/package-lock.json

# Playwright MCP server run artifacts (ephemeral, machine-local)
.playwright-mcp/

# web/ runtime cache — cached company logo images, not personal data, not worth versioning
.career-ops-web/

# Planning (local scratchpad)
plan/
